newsBot gathers news from various news feeds(RDF/RSS-pages) and send the news
to your IM client. The bot is a console based application and uses the Jabber
network for messaging.

Each RDF/RSS-page is checked every 30 min in a running order. When a new news
item is found, the news will be sent to the users with the website in its site
list. The news item will include(if available) title, date, link and a short
description.

Features:
    * Individual user settings.
    * 15 bot commands.
    * Over 30 news feeds to choose from.
    * Ability to add and remove news feeds.
    * and more...

WWW: http://newsbot.jabberstudio.org/
